trans-unit.source: Defines the interface that associates an output channel with a session.
trans-unit.target: Define a interface que associa um canal de saída a uma sessão.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputSessionChannel> interface indicates that an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputChannel> implements <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputSession> semantics.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputSessionChannel> interface indica que um <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputChannel> implementa <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputSession> semântica.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputSession> associated with an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputSessionChannel> can be retrieved through the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ISessionChannel%601.Session%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputSession> associado com um <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IOutputSessionChannel> podem ser recuperados por meio de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ISessionChannel%601.Session%2A> propriedade.
